#ad There’s something truly special about a live edge table! When you pair that with @minwaxusa Natural Stain, the wood grain truly comes alive! #woodworking #stainingwood #minwaxpartner

#ad There's something truly special about a live edge table - the organic lines of the wood create a natural and unique piece that brings the beauty of the outdoors inside. And when you pair that with @minwaxusa Natural stain, the wood grain truly comes alive, showcasing its stunning beauty in all its glory. But it doesn't stop there - to ensure your table stands the test of time, be sure to finish it off with a few layers of Polycrylic. This water based topcoat not only adds a beautiful clear finish, but also provides extra protection, ensuring your piece of furniture will last a lifetime. Who else loves a good live edge table? 🌲🪵💛 #liveedgetable #woodworking #minwaxpartner #homedecor #interiordesign #natureinside
